{"tid":619116,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★綜援又win！派錢4000綜援戶First快過其餘237萬香港人！","createTime":"2018-04-06T10:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T05:20:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"481e53acbf44d420a94f7690fefcff7767ee87f2","tid":619116,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T10:57:49.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=8GNVODSvOC4A%2BY92yGhwoPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=8ea811e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】43萬名領取社會保障的人士「自動享」4000港元計劃，<span style=\"color: red;\">快過其餘237萬香港人！</span>不過，其中2萬名綜援戶，獲補回的金額最多480港元，最少只有50港元，即較4000港元最多縮水79倍！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波為財政預算案派糖不勻補鑊，上月公布4000港元「關愛共享」計劃時，明言現時社會保障受惠人士「出三糧」者如領不足4000港元，會補回有關差額。而立法會今日(6日)一份文件披露，有43萬名社會保障人士受惠，其中2萬人領取綜援。<br />\n<br />\n立法會福利事務委員會下周一(9日)會討論上述事宜，根據文件顯示，有3類社會保障人士可領取差額，共涉及4.35億港元公帑。第一類是28萬名俗稱領「生果金」的高齡津貼受惠人，每人可補回1310港元的差額；第二類是13萬名領取普通傷殘津貼人士，每人可補回560港元的差額；第三類則是部分綜援受助人，例如3或4人家庭中的健全成人或兒童，差額由50港元至480港元不等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府預計，上述額外金額最快可於立法會批准草案後的1個月後開始發放，而有關款項會以自動轉賬方式支付予受惠人士，即領款人毋須另行提出申請。當時陳茂波預計，有280萬人可受惠4000港元計劃，扣除上述43萬人後，即其餘237萬人要自行申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/43萬人自動享-4000補差額-綜援戶最少補-50-092911606.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F43%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E4%BA%AB-4000%E8%A3%9C%E5%B7%AE%E9%A1%8D-%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4%E6%88%B6%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%91%E8%A3%9C-50-092911606.html&d=8GNVODSvOC4A%2BY92yGhwoPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=e3ecb36d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/43萬人自動享-4000補差額-綜援戶最少補-50-092911606.html</a>"},{"pid":"29de7d8519ff160701f35a95e7d17d405793f6b1","tid":619116,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T10:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108dce65340168fe5c0dcda853bd2021d1d36316","tid":619116,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"果然 得綜援 得天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3067c68623b8bad5060d28fbdf4485b52ccefde","tid":619116,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:00:54.000Z","msg":"「出三糧」者如領不足4000港元，會補回有關差額。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2149f8f03fcb791a33837604f6b22c839b7049c","tid":619116,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:10:31.000Z","msg":"老貓正一仆街仔黎"},{"pid":"c0dee2afcb197eb926b02296e7137b21f030468b","tid":619116,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3067c68623b8bad5060d28fbdf4485b52ccefde","tid":619116,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:00:54.000Z","msg":"「出三糧」者如領不足4000港元，會補回有關差額。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T12:55:51.000Z","msg":"4糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7d49e43385439972ee269705172ceee332a78a","tid":619116,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T12:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓豬=蝗蟲"},{"pid":"e9b02c0fc0fe4a5dd89c2da31cef7382411355bd","tid":619116,"uid":24660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eb7d49e43385439972ee269705172ceee332a78a","tid":619116,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T12:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓豬=蝗蟲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:05:26.000Z","msg":"講中樓豬死穴"},{"pid":"88eb3a376b854190c127931b7c6e8373f21bd998","tid":619116,"uid":17738,"li